      "instruction": "<p><span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>Now let's get started!</strong></span></p>\n<p>Boil a kettle</p>\n<p>Heat a <span class=\"text-highlight\">large,</span> wide-based pan<span class=\"text-highlight\"> (preferably non-stick with a matching lid)</span> with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Slice</span> the <strong>spring onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> finely</p>",
