      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong> and <strong>thyme</strong> <span class=\"text-highlight\">(no need to pick the leaves) to the pan </span></p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Season with</span> a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for<span class=\"text-highlight\"> 1-2 min</span> or until fragrant and starting to soften</p>",
